:R-HSA-167044  a            obo:GO_0007265 , owl:NamedIndividual ;
        rdfs:comment        "Signalling through Shc adaptor proteins appears to be identical for both NGF and EGF. It leads to a fast, but transient, MAPK/ERK activation, which is insufficient to explain the prolonged activation of MAPK found in NGF-treated cells." ;
        rdfs:label          "Signalling to RAS" ;
